Description: Providers billing intravitreal injections (67028) and E/M codes (99202 to 99215) on the same claim; flagged if in the top 10% by paid amount.
Providers with high paid amounts for selected skin graft/substitute codes (Q4164, Q4186, Q4205, Q4217, Q4253); flagged if in the top 10%.
Providers billing intravitreal injections (67028) with drug J-codes but without relevant ophthalmologic diagnoses; flagged if in the top 10% by paid amount.
Providers billing DME (L-codes) where the member state differs from the provider state.
